So, I went ahead and made a song on my own. Would you like to hear it?

789
01:00:19,565 --> 01:00:21,165
食べながらでいいんで。
You can listen while you eat.

790
01:00:20,165 --> 01:00:22,165
食べながら聞くの！？
While eating!?

791
01:00:22,165 --> 01:00:25,665
はい！それでは、聞いてください！
